<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"
    />
    <meta name="description" content="" />
    <meta name="author" content="" />
    <title>Web322 Assignment 5</title>
    <!-- Favicon-->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/web_logo.png" />
    <!-- Bootstrap icons-->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Responsive navbar-->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/read_more">Article Page</a>
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/read_more"
                >Article</a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/registration">Create an account</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Sign in to WHC</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- Page content-->
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <!-- Post content-->
          <article>
            <!-- Post header-->
            <header class="mb-4">
              <!-- Post title-->
              <h1 class="fw-bolder mb-1">
                {{title}}
              </h1>
              <!-- Post meta content-->
              <div class="text-muted fst-italic mb-2">
                {{date}}
              </div>
            </header>
            <!-- Preview image figure-->
            <figure class="mb-4">
              <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="{{image}}" alt="..." />
            </figure>
            <!-- Post content-->
            <section class="mb-5">
              <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
                {{read}}
              </p>
            </section>
          </article>
          <br/><br/>
          <section class="mb-5">
              <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
                To update the article, please fill the form below!
              </p>
          </section>
          <form action="/update" method="post" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded">
            <input type="hidden" name="ids" id="ids" value="{{id}}">
              <div class="container bg-light">
                <div class="p-3 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-check">
                    <label for="title">Title:</label>
                    <input class="form-control" type="text" name="title" id="title">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-check">
                    <label for="dat">Date:</label>
                    <input class="form-control" type="text" name="dat" id="dat">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-check">
                    <label for="content">Content:</label>
                    <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-check">
                    <label for="img">Image:</label>
                    <input list="images" id="img" name="img"><br><br>
                    <datalist id="images">
                        <option value="bird.jpg">
                        <option value="lion.jpg">
                        <option value="penguin.jpg">
                        <option value="flower.jpg">
                    </datalist>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-3 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Update</button>
                </div>
              </div>
          </form>
          <!-- Comments section-->
          <section class="mb-5">
            <div class="card bg-light">
              <div class="card-body">
                <!-- Comment form-->
                <form class="mb-4">
                  <textarea
                    class="form-control"
                    rows="3"
                    placeholder="Join the discussion and leave a comment!"
                  ></textarea
                  ><button
                    class="btn btn-primary"
                    id="button-search"
                    type="button"
                  >
                    Submit!
                  </button>
                </form>
                <!-- Comment with nested comments-->
                <div class="d-flex mb-4">
                  <!-- Parent comment-->
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                    <img
                      class="rounded-circle"
                      src="https://dummyimage.com/50x50/ced4da/6c757d.jpg"
                      alt="..."
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="ms-3">
                    <div class="fw-bold">MajManiak</div>
                    If anything Neon Genesis Evangelion should be on the list.
                    For people that personally experienced the themes of the
                    series the show is beyond just entertainment, it's
                    absolutely therapeutic.
                    <!-- Child comment 1-->
                    <div class="d-flex mt-4">
                      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <img
                          class="rounded-circle"
                          src="https://dummyimage.com/50x50/ced4da/6c757d.jpg"
                          alt="..."
                        />
                      </div>
                      <div class="ms-3">
                        <div class="fw-bold">Yummysundae</div>
                        I am so happy One Punch Man is on this list. I'm not
                        huge into anime so I don't exactly know how well known
                        One Punch Man is to most people. If anyone is looking
                        for a nice one season incredible anime to get into, I
                        cannot recommend One Punch Man enough.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Child comment 2-->
                    <div class="d-flex mt-4">
                      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <img
                          class="rounded-circle"
                          src="https://dummyimage.com/50x50/ced4da/6c757d.jpg"
                          alt="..."
                        />
                      </div>
                      <div class="ms-3">
                        <div class="fw-bold">Umar Khan</div>
                        I would recommend people to watch Assassination
                        classroom as well since it has a very good story along
                        with fights, comedy, drama. its a must watch from me :)
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Single comment-->
                <div class="d-flex">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                    <img
                      class="rounded-circle"
                      src="https://dummyimage.com/50x50/ced4da/6c757d.jpg"
                      alt="..."
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="ms-3">
                    <div class="fw-bold">RebelScum1138</div>
                    Monster is incredible, wish it was more widely available so
                    people could watch it.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
        <!-- Side widgets-->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <!-- Search widget-->
          <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-header">Search</div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="input-group">
                <input
                  class="form-control"
                  type="text"
                  placeholder="Enter search term..."
                  aria-label="Enter search term..."
                  aria-describedby="button-search"
                />
                <button
                  class="btn btn-primary"
                  id="button-search"
                  type="button"
                >
                  Go!
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Categories widget-->
          <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-header">Categories as per wikipedia</div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                    <li><a href="/blog">Blogs</a></li>
                    <li>
                      <a
                        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_action_anime#:~:text=List%20of%20action%20anime%20%20%20%20English,%20Yuzuru%20Tachikawa%20%2015%20more%20rows%20"
                        >Action</a
                      >
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <a
                        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_drama_anime#:~:text=List%20of%20drama%20anime%20%20%20%20Year,%20Studio%20Deen%20%2020%20more%20rows%20"
                        >Drama</a
                      >
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                    <li>
                      <a
                        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_romance_anime#:~:text=List%20of%20romance%20anime%20%20%20%20English,%20%20JA%2FEN%20%2037%20more%20rows%20"
                        >Romance</a
                      >
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <a
                        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_slice_of_life_anime#:~:text=List%20of%20slice%20of%20life%20anime%20%20,%20Silver%20Link%20%2026%20more%20rows%20"
                        >Slice Of life</a
                      >
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <a
                        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_comedy_anime"
                        >Comedy</a
                      >
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Side widget-->
          <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-header">
              Personal experience of watching anime.
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              In my life up until this point I have successfully completed upto
              192 animes which includes multiple genres such as action,
              thriller, comedy, romance, slice of life. It started when I first
              came across Naruto in my childhood. For some reason I use to
              relate to the anime and mainly the characters which not only
              helped me mature, but look at the world in a different way and I
              am happy that I came across them.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
